snippet.title: LOONEY LANDERS | arcade party game | launch trailer | ルーニー・ランダース
snippet.description:
Landing Feb 5, 2025!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3169660/Looney_Landers/

Looney Landers is a fast-paced arcade party game for 1-2 players. Skydive into a whirlwind of chaos as you compete against friends, family, or the CPU to claim the top spot on the leaderboards in this score-chasing frenzy!

- Versus Mode: P1 vs P2 or P1 vs CPU
- Difficulty Options: Easy & Hard modes
- Retro Graphics: Vibrant 4-bit pixel art
- Great Chiptunes: Original OPL FM music by naruto2413
- Arcade Bezel: Illustration by Pete Ellison
- Global Competition: Worldwide leaderboards

Steam, AtariVCS
#arcade #retro #atari
